834
01:18:10,311 --> 01:18:11,477
Keep an eye on it.

835
01:18:13,055 --> 01:18:14,708
So you remember me sometimes.

836
01:18:17,204 --> 01:18:20,651
What are you thinking?

837
01:18:21,757 --> 01:18:22,377
Say it.

838
01:18:24,285 --> 01:18:26,078
