839
01:18:28,481 --> 01:18:29,554
But.

840
01:18:31,027 --> 01:18:31,614
But?

841
01:18:33,875 --> 01:18:38,741
It's just... it's sad not seeing your face.

842
01:19:03,692 --> 01:19:04,899
Are you mad?

843
01:19:06,338 --> 01:19:07,665
No.

844
01:19:08,351 --> 01:19:09,758
