845
01:19:11,664 --> 01:19:12,431
Thanks.

846
01:19:17,878 --> 01:19:19,152
I'll have it.

847
01:19:19,923 --> 01:19:20,529
You can't drink.

848
01:19:20,589 --> 01:19:21,696
